你識少少扮代表啦<br />\n中國sovereign rating 係A1/A+呀懵撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩評國企同其他企業係兩標準又係on9<br />\n只係國企rating 用scorecard計完會apply uplift<br />\n但點up都唔會係高過sovereign rating 囉<br />\n仲未計要分central sasac 定local sasac<br />\n唔否認中國未必係咁有錢 但你都唔好當bank 同rating agency係傻閪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}